======================================================================
 - Add the following line to /etc/rc.conf to enable cdrd:

     cdrd_enable="YES"

 - A symbolic link to %%ETCDIR%%/cdrd.newsyslog.conf
   has been created in the /usr/local/etc/newsyslog.conf.d directory.
   You can edit %%ETCDIR%%/cdrd.newsyslog.conf
   to change log file rotation configuration.
